Indisputably, no human is limited. Eliud Kipchoge’s Ineos 1:59 challenge reminds us that we should race against the targets we set for ourselves amid our vision and life mission. Hence, we should not be drawn away by the noise around us. The main reason why most people don’t succeed in life is that they err to acknowledge themselves. Kipchoge’s testimony enlists the league of Former US president Barrack Obama who said ‘yes we can ‘ and our very own Hollywood star Lupita Nyon’go who said that ‘all dreams are valid’.  Mombasa